enable cpu virtialization ->
      enable or close windows function menu , to enable WSL function.
install ubuntu20.04.6 LTS ->
      windows app store search and install.
usb/ip install ->
      host ->
          winget install --interactive --exact dorssel.usbipd-win
          usbipd list
          usbipd bind --busid <BUSID>
          usbipd attach --wsl --busid <BUSID>

          demo
              PS C:\Windows\system32> usbipd list
